<h2>Keyword Strategy: Target Buyers, Not Browsers</h2>
<p>Most SEO traffic does not convert because most keyword strategies target the wrong intent. Ranking for "what is project management" brings researchers. Ranking for "project management software for construction teams" brings buyers.</p>
<h3>Map Keywords to the Buyer Journey</h3>
<p>Every keyword sits somewhere on the buyer journey. Your strategy should target keywords across all stages, with the highest priority on bottom-of-funnel terms.</p>
